1.患者女性，54岁，既往否认高血压病、糖尿病病史。2.主要症状：头晕、头痛、腰痛为主症，时有视物旋转，头部沉重感，头痛如刺，位置不固定，巅顶为重，颈部酸痛不适，胃脘部时有不适，腰痛，劳累后加重，平卧后好转，饮食欠佳，睡眠不实，无发热及畏寒， 无恶心、呕吐及腹泻等症状。3.查体：&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;T 36.5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;℃、&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P80&lt;/span&gt;次∕分、&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;R18&lt;/span&gt;次∕分、&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;BP110/60mmHg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;'&gt;咽部无充血，口唇无紫绀，五官端正，两肺呼吸动度一致，语颤一致，听诊两肺呼吸音清，两肺听诊未闻及啰音。颈部活动受限，屈曲30&deg;，伸展30&deg;，左侧屈35&deg;，右侧屈30&deg;，左旋转50&deg;，右旋转55&deg;，腰部活动轻度受限，直腿抬高试验阳性。余未见异常。神经系统检查未见明显异常。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4.辅助检查：颈椎正侧位片示：颈椎退行性改变。头颅CT示：头颅CT平扫示未见明显异常。心电图示：1.完全性右束支传导阻滞。2.重度电轴右偏3.异常心电图。心脏彩超示：心脏结构及血流未见异常。腹部彩超示：双肾、膀胱、子宫及双附件区未见明显异常，双侧输尿管无扩张。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;